[23:09:20] [req:65] in en->ru: "On the 6th of Tuum Ut, you arrive at the oasis-hamlet of Joppa, along the far rim of Moghra'yi, the Great Salt Desert.\n\nAll aраунд you, moisture farmers tend to groves of viridian watervine. There are huts wrought from rock salt and brine...(truncated)"
